Disodium hydrogen phosphate (Na2HPO4), sodium di-hydrogen phosphate (NaH2PO
                           4
                        ), Potassium dihydrogen phosphate (KH2PO4), Hydrogen chloride (HCl), Sodium hydroxide (NaOH), MgSO4 and Glacial acetic acid were purchased from Sigma. AgNO3, CdCl2, Mg(OAc)2, NiCl2, FeCl2, Hg(NO3)2, Pb(NO3)2, and ZnCl2 obtained from Alfa aesar. Na2SO4, NaCl, KCl, CaCl2, CuCl2, MnCl2 obtained from Merck. CoCl2 was obtained from J.T. baker. All aqueous solutions were prepared using ultrapure deionized water from a Milli-Q purification system (Millipore, Milford, MA, USA).
